        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "\n",
        "numeric_columns = df.select_dtypes(include=['int64', 'float64']).columns\n",
        "\n",
        "Q1 = df[numeric_columns].quantile(0.25)\n",
        "Q3 = df[numeric_columns].quantile(0.75)\n",
        "\n",
        "IQR = Q3 - Q1\n",
        "\n",
        "lower_bound = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR\n",
        "upper_bound = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR\n",
        "\n",
        "df_no_outliers = df[~((df[numeric_columns] < lower_bound) | (df[numeric_columns] > upper_bound)).any(axis=1)]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Number of rows before removing outliers: {df.shape[0]}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Number of rows after removing outliers: {df_no_outliers.shape[0]}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Number of rows removed: {df.shape[0] - df_no_outliers.shape[0]}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(15, 10))\n",
        "num_plots = len(numeric_columns)\n",
        "num_rows = 3\n",
        "num_cols = (num_plots - 1) // num_rows + 1\n",
        "\n",
        "for i, col in enumerate(numeric_columns, start=1):\n",
        "    plt.subplot(num_rows, num_cols, i)\n",
        "    sns.boxplot(y=df_no_outliers[col])\n",
        "    plt.title(col)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ]

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier, GradientBoostingClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.svm import SVC\n",
        "from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score\n",
        "\n",
        "# Define and fit models\n",
        "models = {\n",
        "    \"Random Forest\": RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100, random_state=42),\n",
        "    \"Decision Tree\": DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=42),\n",
        "    \"SVM\": SVC(),\n",
        "    \"Gradient Boosting\": GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=42),\n",
        "    \"KNN\": KNeighborsClassifier(),\n",
        "    \"Optimized Decision Tree\": DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=5, min_samples_split=10, random_state=42),\n",
        "    \"Optimized Random Forest\": RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100, max_depth=5, random_state=42),\n",
        "    \"Tuned Gradient Boosting\": GradientBoostingClassifier(n_estimators=200, learning_rate=0.1, max_depth=5,\n",
        "                                                          min_samples_split=5, min_samples_leaf=2, random_state=42)\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "accuracies = [accuracy_score(y_test, model.fit(X_train, y_train).predict(X_test)) for model in models.values()]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plotting\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
        "plt.bar(models.keys(), accuracies, color='purple')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Models')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Accuracy')\n",
        "plt.title('Comparison of Model Accuracies')\n",
        "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
        "plt.ylim(0, 1)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Annotate bars\n",
        "for i, acc in enumerate(accuracies):\n",
        "    plt.text(i, acc + 0.02, f'{acc:.2f}', ha='center')\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
